The uncertainties in our work result from:
* the coincidence sum effect of cascade gamma-ray,
The total uncertainty in each cross section was
obtained by combining the individual uncertainties in
quadrature. The uncertainties in isomeric cross
section ratios should generally be smaller than those
in absolute cross sections, since uncertainties in
monitor reaction cross sections and background neutron
contributions have not to be taken into account.
